 {
  "text": "Hi, everyone. My name is David. I am the new partner at the company. I am from Canada, but now I am in Sao Paulo. I am very happy to be here with the finance team. This is my first week. I want to meet everyone. So please, come and say hello. Tell me your name and what you do. How are you today? I am great, and I am ready to work with you. Welcome to a new year for our team!",
